<form markdown="1" method="POST" action="/update.php" target="progressFrame">
<input type="hidden" name="#file" value="<?=$plugin?>/<?=$plugin?>.cfg">

_(Activity display style)_:
: <select name="display">
  <?=mk_option($cfg['display'], "bar", _("Text with styled bar"))?>
  <?=mk_option($cfg['display'], "color", _("Text with color"))?>
  <?=mk_option($cfg['display'], "plain", _("Plain text"))?>
  </select>

> Choose how disk activity is shown in the Array/Pool device tables.
>
> **Text with styled bar** shows a color-coded progress bar with percentage overlay.
>
> **Text with color** shows the percentage number colored by activity level.
>
> **Plain text** shows just the percentage number with no styling.

<input type="submit" name="#default" value="_(Default)_">
: <input type="submit" name="#apply" value="_(Apply)_"><input type="button" value="_(Done)_" onclick="done()">
</form>
